%% Diagram: Ride Request Sequence
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant R as Rider
    participant Ride as Ride Svc
    participant Px as Pricing
    participant DISCO
    participant Loc as Location
    participant ETA as DeepETA
    participant D as Driver

    R->>Ride: POST /rides
    Ride->>Px: getUpfrontFare
    Px-->>Ride: fare + surge
    Ride->>DISCO: enqueue(rideId)
    Note over DISCO: buffer ~150ms
    DISCO->>Loc: k-ring(pickup, ~3km)
    Loc-->>DISCO: nearby drivers
    DISCO->>ETA: predict ETA per pair
    ETA-->>DISCO: ETAs (sub-5ms)
    Note over DISCO: bipartite assign
    DISCO-->>Ride: matched driver + ETA
    Ride-->>R: 201 Created
    Ride->>D: dispatch(rideId, pickup)
